Technology Stack

| Part | Technology | Reason |
|------|------------|--------|
| Backend | Django (Python) | Handles all business logic, APIs, database, and authentication. |
| Frontend | React (JavaScript) | Builds the user interface and communicates with the backend via API. |
| Database | PostgreSQL | Stores all system data reliably with support for relationships. |
| Authentication | JWT Tokens | Secure login that works well between React and Django. |
| Version Control | Git and GitHub | Tracks all code changes and allows team collaboration. |


